This file will have the require tables for the database.
Abart please check this file regularly and update the database using the migration.php

All ids should be unsigned int.

Tables needed
1. users table
   -userId, firstname, lastname, phone, email, password, preferredArticleTopics (should be a varchar), isSubscribed (integer)

2. ArticleTopics
   -aTopicId, topic, created_at, updated_at

3. Article table
   -articleId, writerId (foreign key referencing the userId), title (varchar 255) not null, subtitle (varchar 255 ), body TEXT not null, publishStatus(published, draft), shares (int), created_at, updated_at, published_at

4. ArticleReaction table
   aReactionId, -articleId (foreign key), applaudedBy (foreign key userId), 

5. Reading table
    -readingId, readerId (userId), articleId, timeReading

6. ArticleTags //new
   -tagRefId, articleId (foreign key), tagId (foreign key from the ArticleTopics table)

7. ArticleKeywords
 -keywordId, articleId, keywords, is_indexed default = 0

8. index 
   -termId, term (varchar(255)), docfreq (int unsigned)

9. temporaryImage
    -tmpImgId, imagePath, created_at